_sText:
This is just a small funny map without any light-entities.
You can also play the map with bots, but be careful, they will be VERY confused xD

I thought about adding an overview, but it wouldn't really help, because you won't see much more than the uppest level of the map. And the map includes 4 levels + ground.

So, try it out, and much fun.^^

Edit: If you really play the map with 40 mates, than start praying, because they will shoot away the floor your walking on xD


P.Panda (Burnixx)
